<p><a href="https://github.com/cjbassi/gotop/">gotop</a> is a system monitor that runs through the terminal for Linux and macOS. The software is inspired by gtop and <a href="https://github.com/MrRio/vtop">vtop</a>, but while these two utilities use Node.js, gotop is written in <a href="https://golang.org/">Go</a>.</p>

<!-- RETANGULO LARGO 2 -->
